The '''''Webley''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Starship/Legends|starship]] which fought at the [[Battle of Yaga Minor (Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Yaga Minor]] near the end of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was under the command of [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Alexandra Winger|Alex Winger]].

